metadata.name: missing children argument
metadata.description:
Rikona, the yellow-haired girl, has been gone since 2006, with another six children born at the same time. The yellow-haired girl walks slowly with no destination.

"Who made me like this?"




She questioned herself calmly but angrily as she walked into the little town cornor and discovered that Reta, the daughter of a big mafia in Tokyo, had pushed the little black-haired girl named Reta into the cornor with angry emotions and put any weapon she took with her into her pharynx, as well as a gun.

"Give my old life back!"

"Then try to steal it again AHAHA!"

2487 x 1447 px 300 dpi
